Package edu.temple.capstone.BinBotServer.mobileInterface

Class AppMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.temple.capstone.BinBotServer.mobileInterface.AppMessage
  • public class AppMessage
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to communicate between the BinBot mobile application and the server. It is used for both alerting the Server to stop operation and for sending images to display to the app. It is sent as a json string in the format { "poweredState":, "img": } where poweredState is true when the system should continue operation and the img is a BufferedImage converted into a string which will be displayed in the mobile application.
    Since:
    2019-10-29
